Description: GDG New Delhi is proud to present DevFest 2023, the biggest event of the year for developers, designers, and techies. This one-day festival will feature multiple tracks of tech sessions, communities, and projects, as well as food and fun activities. Whether you're a seasoned pro or just getting started in the tech world, DevFest has something for everyone. So mark your calendars, wear a big smile and we'll see you there!

DevFest Mangalore 2023 will be the largest technical event and the first ever GDG festival in Mangalore as we set to host 1000+ developers from various geographies including Mangalore, Udupi, and Kasargod. Our day will be overloaded with knowledge and fun as we have speaker sessions from Googlers and Google Developer Experts, hands-on workshops on trending topics like GenAI and Kubernetes, IAMRemarkable session for empowerment and a lot of time and space for networking!
